message.msgid: WAN port bandwidth can not be empty!
The value of bandwidth should not be 0! Please enter a valid bandwidth value.
message.msgstr: 带宽数值不能为0！请输入一个有效的带宽数值。

message.msgid: Up to %s bandwidth control entries can be added.
message.msgstr: 最多可添加%s条带宽控制规则。

message.msgid: Please enter a valid IP address!
message.msgstr: 请输入一个有效的IP地址。

message.msgid: Start IP should not be greater than End IP! Please enter valid IP information.
message.msgstr: 起始IP不能大于终止IP！请输入有效的IP信息。

message.msgid: Please enter a valid bandwidth value!
message.msgstr: 请输入一个有效的带宽数值。

message.msgid: The port is beyond the range of 0~65535!
Starting bandwidth value should not be greater than ending bandwidth!
message.msgstr: 带宽输入范围必须由小到大。

message.msgid: The same IP address can't be contained in two Bandwidth control rules, please retry.
message.msgstr: 已存在同样的配置信息，或者您配置的信息有重叠。请重新输入！

message.msgid: Giving up :(Cannot create an XMLHTTP instance!)
There was a problem with the request.
Information: the security setting is automatically set to WPS,but you can manually modify it.
message.msgstr: 提示：安全设置自动设为WPS ，\n 你也可以手动进行更改。

message.msgid: notag is not allowed to be set to be policy Name!
message.msgstr: notag不允许被设置为策略名称

message.msgid: You must set at least one rule when you choose Permit Only!
message.msgstr: 选择“仅允许”后，您必须设置至少一条规则。

message.msgid: Start IP should not be greater than end IP. Please enter a valid IP address.
message.msgstr: 起始IP必须大于终止IP。请输入有效的IP地址。

message.msgid: Please specify a valid MAC address!
Please enter a valid keyword or domain name.
message.msgstr: 请输入有效的关键字或域名。
起始时间必须早于终止时间！规则的时间段不能跨过00:00。
起始星期必须小于终止星期！（星期日~星期六）请重试。
开始端口不能大于结束端口。请输入1~65535之间是有效值。

message.msgid: The Remote Management IP address should not be on the same IP net segment as the router's LAN IP,please enter a valid IP address.
message.msgstr: 远程管理IP地址不能与路由器登录IP地址在同一网段。请重新输入一个有效的IP地址。
